 Allows users to create accounts and log in securely
Home Page / Facility Browsing Page:
 Displays available sports facilities with filtering options
Booking Page:
 Allows users to select a facility, date, and time slot and make reservations
User Dashboard:
 Shows booking history, upcoming reservations, and options to modify or cancel bookings
Admin Dashboard:
 Allows administrators to manage facilities, users, schedules, and view reports
The interface is responsive and works on both desktop and mobile devices.
e. Security Measures
The system implements several security measures to protect user data and ensure safe operation:
Authentication:
 Users must log in with email and password to access the system
Password Encryption:
 Passwords are encrypted before being stored in the database
Role-Based Access Control:
 Different roles (admin, user, staff) have different permissions
Data Protection:
 Sensitive data is protected from unauthorized access
Session Management:
 User sessions expire after a period of inactivity
These measures ensure that the system is secure, reliable, and compliant with basic data protection standards.
